<h5>Inline Help &amp; Documentation:</h5>
<p>We have jam packed extensive documentation into Morph, explaining each and every option that is available.</p>

<h5>Beta Testers Support Board:</h5>
<p>We have added a special beta testers board to our forum, where you can submit any bugs you find, provide us with feedback or share an idea you may have on how we can make Morph even better. <a href="http://www.joomlajunkie.com/members/morph" target="_blank">Start posting</a>.</p>

<h5>Morph Documentation Site:</h5>
<p>The online documentation site will grow extensively over the next couple of months, with everything from documenting every aspect of Morph, extensive tutorials, screencasts &amp; more. <a href="http://www.joomlajunkie.com/morph2" target="_blank">Check it out</a>.</p>

<h5>Twitter Updates:</h5>
<p>We want to be incredibly easy for you to stay informed about Morphs progress, so we have created a twitter account just for MorphUpdates. Follow this account to get up to the minute updates. <a href="http://twitter.com/jMorph" target="_blank">Follow @jMorph</a> on Twitter.</p>